OL,3,CJersey's only major brewery to close
OL,4,Cand move production to Somerset
OL,6,FJersey's only major brewery will close
OL,7,Fand relocate production to Somerset in
OL,8,Fa bid to safeguard its future.
OL,10,FLiberation Brewing Co has prided
OL,11,Fitself on making beers locally for
OL,12,Fnearly 150 years and even continued
OL,13,Foperations through both World Wars.
OL,15,FHowever, its UK parent company, the
OL,16,FButcombe Group, says costs have
OL,17,F"dramatically risen over the last few
OL,18,Fyears" and it is no longer viable to
OL,19,Frun the brewery at Tregear House in St
OL,20,FSaviour.
