OL,3,CJersey's only major brewery to close
OL,4,Cand move production to Somerset
OL,6,FSome job losses are expected, although
OL,7,Fthe exact figure is not yet known as a
OL,8,Fconsultation is ongoing.
OL,10,FButcombe says it is working with its
OL,11,FJersey team "to explore options and
OL,12,Fprovide support through this
OL,13,Ftransitional period".
OL,15,FThe existing on-island warehouse,
OL,16,Fdistribution business and offices at
OL,17,FTregear House, as well as the
OL,18,FLiberation shop opposite on
OL,19,FLongueville Road, will be unaffected.
