OL,3,CJersey's only major brewery to close
OL,4,Cand move production to Somerset
OL,6,FOn concerns over changes in the supply
OL,7,Fchain, Butcombe explains: "We are
OL,8,Fputting safeguards in place to avoid
OL,9,Fthis and will be making sure we
OL,10,Fcommunicate with all our customers to
OL,11,Fminimise any impact."
OL,13,FPat Dean, Head Brewer of Liberation
OL,14,FBrewing Co, will move from Jersey to
OL,15,FSomerset and continue to oversee the
OL,16,Fproduction of Liberation Ales.
