OL,3,CJersey's only major brewery to close
OL,4,Cand move production to Somerset
OL,6,FThe Head Brewer of Butcombe Group,
OL,7,FMike Jordan, says: "I'm really excited
OL,8,Fabout the move to Somerset and the
OL,9,Fopportunity to help preserve the
OL,10,Flegacy of Liberation Brewery.
OL,12,F"This move allows us to continue
OL,13,Fbrewing some of the best ales in the
OL,14,Fworld and to further develop our small
OL,15,Fbatch cask programme."
OL,17,FThe firm explains that it will
OL,18,Fcontinue to brew Liberation beers
OL,19,Fusing the same recipes and ingredients.
