OL,6,FWhile some equipment is being moved
OL,7,Fover to the UK so it can still be
OL,8,Fused, Butcombe says it is working with
OL,9,Flocal museums to donate other items
OL,10,Fthat reflect Jersey's brewing history.
OL,12,FThe company adds that these changes
OL,13,Fwill not see prices increase and the
OL,14,FLiberation brand will continue.
